item.title: CVE-2010-4657|2024-08-07T03:51:17.954Z -- php5 -- php5
item.description: PHP5 before 5.4.4 allows passing invalid utf-8 strings via the xmlTextWriterWriteAttribute, which are then misparsed by libxml2. This results in memory leak into the resulting output.
